      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6b9034fe-c527-11e2-b5f5-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
